  "texts": [
    "While Claude 2 may not yet match the capabilities of GPT-4, it is rapidly advancing and consistently outperforms most other AI models in standardized tests.",
    "Claude 2 distinguishes itself with its capacity to manage up to 100K tokens per prompt, equivalent to approximately 75,000 words.",
    "This is a twelve-fold increase compared to the standard amount offered by GPT-4.",
    "Also, while GPT's knowledge cutoff is September 2021, Claude 2 benefits from training data extending up to early 2023 [8].",
    "Anthropic unveiled Claude 2.1 on November 23, 2023, marking the newest update to their LLM lineup."
  ],
